{"title":"诗传单","authors":["蒋维","沙柳","桂笑"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":9,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为“草木篇”作者造像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋维"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他与祖国势不两立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“宁愿去资本主义国家作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个自由的贫困儿……”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他与人民不共戴天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要去沙漠里繁殖着儿女…”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一副奴颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一副媚像；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脸横肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身刺刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不交代自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽来批判旁人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"企图制造假象："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是反右尖兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无非是想迷惑人们的眼睛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想        桂笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狡猾的狐狸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想骗过皎洁的月牙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘶哑的乌鸦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想遮住半个天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒蛇的臭蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想把岩石碰垮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丑恶的癞蛤蟆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想取下大象的牙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载“江西日报”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}